FBIS3-22913 "jptot008__l94013" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Gunmen Hold Four Hostage in Durban House of Delegates Hostage Drama Ends; 12 Arrested MB1002203294 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 2000 GMT 10 Feb 94 MB1002203294 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The hostage drama at Truro House in Durban is over. Twelve people were arrested a short while ago after the hostages were released. The drama started early this afternoon when three House of Delegates employees were taken hostage by a group of seven (Bunela) residents at Truro House. They demanded that charges of trespassing against them be dropped. They had been charged with illegally occupying houses at Cato Manor near Durban. The suspects will appear in court tomorrow.
